@chrome109
Copy content of Razor1911 folder to the game installation dir and overwrite if needed.

then do the same for the missing file

@forpittysake
Double click on the "Crack" folder then double click on the Razor1911 folder. Select both folders in there then right click and select Copy. Now goto "My Computer" or "Computer" in the start menu. Double click on "C: Local Disk", double click "Program Files", double click "2k games", double click "BioShock 2". Now right click on a empty space in that folder and select Paste and overwrite all files. Now go back to the missing file folder and copy Bioshock2Launcher.exe to "2K Games\BioShock 2\SP\Builds\Binaries".

I would like some delicious cake :)
